383
00:17:48.693 --> 00:17:51.365
（笑声）
(Laughter)

384
00:17:51.365 --> 00:17:54.017
另一个人是爱迪生，
The other person there is Edison,

385
00:17:54.017 --> 00:17:57.577
经常被嘲讽说他是一个单调乏味的人，
who is actually often vilified for being kind of pedestrian

386
00:17:57.577 --> 00:17:59.522
而且——
and is --

387
00:17:59.522 --> 00:18:02.259
他最有名的一句话就是，
I mean, his most famous quote is,

388
00:18:02.259 --> 00:18:07.396
“天才是1%的灵感加上99%的汗水。”
"Genius is one percent inspiration and 99 percent perspiration."

389
00:18:07.396 --> 00:18:08.906
而我是爱迪生一派的，
And I'm in the Edison camp,

390
00:18:08.906 --> 00:18:11.115
尽管人们经常讨厌他。
even if people don't always like him.

391
00:18:11.115 --> 00:18:14.137
如果你比较一下这两位，
Because if you actually compare the two,

392
00:18:14.137 --> 00:18:18.704
特斯拉很能抓眼球，
Tesla has kind of this mind grab these days,

393
00:18:18.704 --> 00:18:21.853
但真正改变世界的是谁？
but who actually changed the world?

394
00:18:21.853 --> 00:18:25.315
爱迪生也许不是个讨喜的人，
Edison may not have been a nice person,

395
00:18:25.315 --> 00:18:28.431
但他做了很多事——
he did a lot of things --

396
00:18:28.431 --> 00:18:30.884
他也许没那么天才，
he was maybe not so intellectual,

397
00:18:30.884 --> 00:18:34.355
不是那么有远见。
not so visionary.

398
00:18:34.355 --> 00:18:37.670
我觉得自己更像爱迪生而不是特斯拉。
But I think I'm more of an Edison than a Tesla.

399
00:18:37.670 --> 00:18:40.136
CA：TED大会这一周的主题是梦想——
