00:18:53.825 --> 00:18:56.055
挣了非常多的钱。
like, billions of dollars out of your software.

408
00:18:56.055 --> 00:18:57.240
你会觉得不爽吗？
Does that piss you off?

409
00:18:57.240 --> 00:18:58.434
LT：不会。
LT: No.

410
00:18:58.434 --> 00:19:01.063
原因有很多，
No, it doesn't piss me off for several reasons.

411
00:19:01.063 --> 00:19:03.116
其中一个原因是，我过得不错。
And one of them is, I'm doing fine.

412
00:19:03.116 --> 00:19:04.942
真心不错。
I'm really doing fine.

413
00:19:04.942 --> 00:19:06.566
另一个原因就是——
But the other reason is --

414
00:19:06.566 --> 00:19:11.916
如果我不将它开源，而过于纠结的话，
