422
00:19:32.950 --> 00:19:34.579
我想这是最后一个话题——
this is, I think we'll end here --

423
00:19:34.579 --> 00:19:38.647
开源软件这个想法已经在全世界实现了吗？
is the open source idea fully realized now in the world,

